OL,3,CDyson to cut around 1,000 jobs across
OL,4,Cthe UK in global restructure
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 people across the UK
OL,7,Fcould lose their jobs at Dyson, as the
OL,8,Fengineering firm looks to restructure
OL,9,Fits global operations.
OL,11,FHundreds of staff at its offices in
OL,12,FBristol and Wiltshire could be
OL,13,Faffected.
OL,15,FThe firm, best known for the invention
OL,16,Fof the bag-less vacuum cleaner, has
OL,17,Fsaid it is responding to global
OL,18,Fmarkets and ensuring its future.
