OL,3,CDyson to cut around 1,000 jobs across
OL,4,Cthe UK in global restructure
OL,6,FDyson CEO, Hanno Kirner said the
OL,7,Fcompany would support those at risk of
OL,8,Fredundancy.
OL,10,FDyson has 3,500 UK employees with
OL,11,Foffices based in Wiltshire, Bristol
OL,12,Fand London.
OL,14,FMr Kirner, said: "We have grown
OL,15,Fquickly and, like all companies, we
OL,16,Freview our global structures from time
OL,17,Fto time to ensure we are prepared for
OL,18,Fthe future.
