OL,6,F"As such, we are proposing changes to
OL,7,Four organisation, which may result in
OL,8,Fredundancies."
OL,10,FHe added the company, which has
OL,11,Foffices in Malmesbury and
OL,12,FHullavington, operates in
OL,13,F"increasingly fierce and competitive
OL,14,Fglobal markets" and they need to be
OL,15,F"entrepreneurial and agile".
OL,17,F"Decisions which impact close and
OL,18,Ftalented colleagues are always
OL,19,Fincredibly painful.
